    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>HELLFIRE RAMPAGE VR</strong>是一款基于动作的战斗游戏，融合了射击和近战格斗机制。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是一位天才的传送门发明家，探测到来自另一个世界的异常信号。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经过调查，你发现地狱生物正在收集魔法水晶精华，准备入侵人类世界。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>-&gt; 你的任务是阻止它们的入侵并收集水晶！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/3548167b1a03b4e7875105a8e8690ff0.poster.avif?t=1737194221\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/3548167b1a03b4e7875105a8e8690ff0.webm?t=1737194221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/3548167b1a03b4e7875105a8e8690ff0.mp4?t=1737194221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用你的<strong>能力</strong>来<strong>减缓时间</strong>，在激烈的战斗中对抗强大的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>[BULLET TIME</i></strong> + <strong><i>DASH]</i></strong>是战术移动和生存的致命组合。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>-&gt; 用任何武器反射子弹！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/3b5e1ebbd6f5d4d5d2d70be2c18fef5d.poster.avif?t=1737194221\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/3b5e1ebbd6f5d4d5d2d70be2c18fef5d.webm?t=1737194221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/3b5e1ebbd6f5d4d5d2d70be2c18fef5d.mp4?t=1737194221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结合魔法棒与护身符，或者将霰弹枪和镰刀结合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发射火球、挥舞光剑、投掷手里剑，甚至演奏恶魔卡林巴琴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >武器库里有丰富的史诗装备，从电锯到弩箭，精彩不断！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>准备好测试超过30种独特武器！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/bf6cfa7e3c708874611109627d74c6a0.poster.avif?t=1737194221\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/bf6cfa7e3c708874611109627d74c6a0.webm?t=1737194221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/bf6cfa7e3c708874611109627d74c6a0.mp4?t=1737194221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对危险的敌群并摧毁它们的源头。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备迎接骷髅、小恶魔、恶魔、地狱猎犬和疯狂乌鸦，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不死召唤王、骷髅女王、巨型恶魔、毒蛾等等...<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/414a253ce680ab4cbe84eb48edf82824.avif?t=1737194221\" width=600 height=346 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>-&gt; 地狱生物不会让你感到无聊！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/e739577d0d8bfd1907d36bf19936a873.poster.avif?t=1737194221\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/e739577d0d8bfd1907d36bf19936a873.webm?t=1737194221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/e739577d0d8bfd1907d36bf19936a873.mp4?t=1737194221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最激动人心、最紧张的战斗正等着你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在不同的神秘地点完成大约<strong>70+</strong>个挑战。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>-&gt; 准备好在致命挑战中挥洒汗水！</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/bf4ac3e709064893e646e8df7044b357.poster.avif?t=1737194221\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/bf4ac3e709064893e646e8df7044b357.webm?t=1737194221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010140/extras/bf4ac3e709064893e646e8df7044b357.mp4?t=1737194221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆 你有足够的勇气挑战<strong>地狱</strong>吗？</p>",
